message.text:
“huh? ano yung logistics and procurement? anong ginagawa nila?”

that was my initial thought upon reading the department description when i was planning to apply as an executive committee.

so bakit ko parin tinuloy yung application ko? simply because i wanted to explore, i wanted to try new things. and i did! literal na nag explore ang gurlypop hahahaha.

so kung gusto mo rin mag compare and contrast ng mga pangalan, mag handle ng parking ng artists, mag charge ng walkie talkies, at mag shopping sa divi, then Logistics and Procurement Department would be so happy to be your home.

kbye

apply na kau hehe
